dered folding and the interaction networks among modules 2, 3 and 4, resulting in reduced conformational dynamics across <sd-pretag id="sdPretag2035786800sd" parent-tag-id="25">BSP</sd-pretag>, hindering its self-assembly and <sd-pretag id="sdPretag786580746sd" type="subcellular" role="component">aggregation</sd-pretag>. <graphic href="https://api.sourcedata.io/file.php?panel_id=109067"/></sd-panel></fig></article>